  <!-- --- HEADER --- -->
  <header class="header">
    <div class="header-top">
      <div>
        <h1 class="name">Basit Masood</h1>
        <div class="title">Head of Product Design</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact">
      <span>Dubai, UAE</span>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <a href="mailto:basitmasood999@gmail.com">basitmasood999@gmail.com</a>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/iabm" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/iabm</a>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <a href="https://abmcooks.github.io" target="_blank">abmcooks.github.io</a>
    </div>
    <p class="summary" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      Head of Product Design with 8 years in fintech, specializing in complex financial products for emerging markets. Founding designer at SadaPay (0&rarr;4M+ users, $1.5B+ annual volume, acquired for $50M) and ZAR (a16z-backed). Built and led design teams of up to 12, created 5 production design systems, and established research, hiring, and governance frameworks from scratch. Engineering background enables deep cross-functional collaboration. Products I&rsquo;ve designed have raised $90M+ in funding.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- --- EXPERIENCE --- -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Experience</div>

    <!-- ZAR -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-header">
        <div>
          <span class="entry-company">ZAR</span>
          <span class="entry-role">&nbsp;&mdash; Head of Product Design</span>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-meta">Nov 2024 &ndash; Present &middot; Dubai</span>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-desc">Founding designer at a Solana-powered digital dollar wallet for emerging markets (a16z crypto, Dragonfly, Coinbase Ventures, VanEck, Solana Ventures &middot; $20M total raised)</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Validated product-market fit through on-ground surveys, interviews with freelancers, remittance centers, and receivers&mdash;uncovered that people hold foreign currency in physical cash to hedge inflation, and that 65%+ of Pakistan&rsquo;s crypto trades are USDT with no legal fiat off-ramp. Findings shaped ZAR&rsquo;s core product direction.</li>
        <li>Led the full brand-to-product pipeline: translated Ragged Edge&rsquo;s (London) brand guidelines into a complete product design language&mdash;screens, components, interactions, and design system&mdash;then worked closely with engineers to ship it into production within weeks</li>
        <li>Built Techtonic design system (670+ components, 37 Figma pages, 3 platforms) with design tokens in code&mdash;enabling zero visual drift across Flutter, React Native, and Web</li>
        <li>Hired and managed 3&ndash;4 designers; established design governance, brand compliance, and UX standards across all product squads. Worked closely with top design agencies including Ragged Edge and ToyFight.</li>
        <li>Reduced user onboarding from 18 steps to 4 (77.8% reduction) by redesigning the Golden Flow&mdash;value-first architecture where users see money before creating an account. Presented to board of directors.</li>
        <li>Redesigned merchant onboarding from 19 steps to 4 using QR-based authless architecture and $5 ghost wallets&mdash;targeting 100,000 merchants with zero employees</li>
        <li>Discovered through field observation that 72% of merchant transactions bypassed the formal order system&mdash;killed the order flow entirely and redesigned around the 3-step physical-first model merchants were already using</li>
        <li>Eliminated design as a bottleneck through three iterations: first built an AI design consultant (Chothu), then automated the full workflow so engineers self-serve directly from the 670-component design system via AI&mdash;no designer needed for MVP screens</li>
        <li>Designed brand identity, IA, and design system for MACHINA&mdash;ZAR&rsquo;s AI-native operating system suite (5 tools: Nexus, Agentus, Empirium, Agora, Eventus) built on the &ldquo;0-Person Company&rdquo; thesis. Primary users are AI agents, secondary users are humans&mdash;designed for both.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- ADIB -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-header">
        <div>
          <span class="entry-company">ADIB (Abu Dhabi Islamic Bank)</span>
          <span class="entry-role">&nbsp;&mdash; Lead Product Designer</span>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-meta">Sep 2024 &ndash; Feb 2025 &middot; Abu Dhabi</span>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-desc">Led product design at one of the world&rsquo;s largest Islamic banks (1M+ registered app users, 1.5M customers, 80% digital adoption), via Synechron. Named &ldquo;Best Bank for Consumers&rdquo; by Euromoney 2025.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Designed end-to-end UX for Remit! (Visa Direct)&mdash;real-time cross-border money transfers reaching 11B+ cards, wallets, and accounts globally. First bank worldwide to offer such reach.</li>
        <li>Designed open banking UI/UX from zero in partnership with Lean Technologies, advancing UAE&rsquo;s Open Finance ecosystem</li>
        <li>Audited and restructured a fragmented design system across all screens&mdash;rebuilt as atomic component library with governance standards and QA processes across all product domains</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- SadaPay -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-header">
        <div>
          <span class="entry-company">SadaPay</span>
          <span class="entry-role">&nbsp;&mdash; UX Designer &rarr; Senior &rarr; Lead &rarr; Head of Product Design</span>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-meta">Dec 2020 &ndash; Aug 2024 &middot; Pakistan</span>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-desc">Founding Product Designer at Pakistan's first neobank. Grew from sole IC to Head of Design, scaling the product from zero users to 4M+ and $1.5B+ annual transaction volume.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Designed the product experience from day one that helped secure $7.2M seed (largest by a Pakistani startup at the time), $20M+ total funding, and a $50M acquisition by Papara. App Store: 4.8&#9733; (11K reviews), Play Store: 4.7&#9733; (50.9K reviews).</li>
        <li>Simplified authentication by challenging assumptions the industry accepted as mandatory&mdash;removed unnecessary PINs, passwords, and OTPs, replacing them with biometric login. SadaPay became the go-to wallet for daily transactions due to speed.</li>
        <li>Designed a gamified waitlist that grew to 700,000+ signups with zero paid acquisition&mdash;Founders Club cards, golden tickets, and referral mechanics. Waitlist users became the highest-transacting cohort post-launch.</li>
        <li>Launched the first numberless debit card in the Middle East and Africa in collaboration with Mastercard&mdash;vertical design, teal and peach colorways. The card became SadaPay&rsquo;s most recognizable brand asset.</li>
        <li>Grew SadaBiz (freelancer payments) transaction volume by 441% ($160K&rarr;$869K/month) and reduced fraud rate by 79% (3.26%&rarr;0.67%) through service design blueprints mapping front-stage and back-stage operations.</li>
        <li>Built Nukta design system with tokens connected to production code&mdash;first design token implementation in Pakistan&rsquo;s fintech. New features shipped 2x faster after adoption.</li>
        <li>Led product strategy across 8+ surfaces: core wallet, SadaBiz, chatbot, Mission Control (internal ops for 50+ associates), SadaSchool, in-app stories, and website (CSS Design Awards Special Kudos).</li>
        <li>Scaled design team from 1&rarr;8: created 4-level career progression framework, 7-stage hiring pipeline, design chapter with weekly crits and quarterly retros. Alumni now at Revolut and other top companies.</li>
        <li>Built a centralized user research practice from scratch&mdash;research repository, UX research toolkit, interview frameworks, and The Mom Test adoption across the entire product org.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Xpence -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-header">
        <div>
          <span class="entry-company">Xpence (via VentureDive)</span>
          <span class="entry-role">&nbsp;&mdash; UX Designer</span>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-meta">Mar 2020 &ndash; Dec 2020 &middot; Dubai</span>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-desc">Smart business spend management tool for UAE SMEs and freelancers. CTO from N26, backed by leading investors.</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Designed the complete fintech app in 8 sprints&mdash;wireframes, UX flows, micro-interactions, and stakeholder presentations to C-level leadership</li>
        <li>Built Xperia design system from scratch using atomic design principles with full documentation and engineering walkthroughs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Vizteck -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-header">
        <div>
          <span class="entry-company">Vizteck Solutions</span>
          <span class="entry-role">&nbsp;&mdash; UI/UX Designer</span>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-meta">Mar 2019 &ndash; Feb 2020 &middot; Islamabad</span>
      </div>
      <div class="consult-desc">Launched design career on ride-hailing (Darkcarz, Whipp), food delivery (MyGroser, FoodXpress), and on-demand service apps (Harecut, Paddle, Noon, Boon4).</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Consulting -->
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 16px;">Selected Consulting</div>

      <div class="consult-entry">
        <div class="consult-header">
          <span class="consult-name">Bolt VPN &mdash; Product Design Consultant</span>
          <span class="consult-meta">Dec 2024 &ndash; Mar 2025 &middot; via Galixo AI</span>
        </div>
        <div class="consult-desc">Led complete UI/UX transformation for VPN app with 25M+ downloads and 1M+ daily users. Redesigned interface, optimized paywall conversion, and built atomic design system across iOS, Android, and Chrome extension.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="consult-entry">
        <div class="consult-header">
          <span class="consult-name">GoCompliance &mdash; Product Design Consultant</span>
          <span class="consult-meta">Aug 2024 &ndash; Jan 2025 &middot; via GoSaaS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="consult-desc">Overhauled UX for Oracle-integrated compliance platform serving Fortune 500 companies. Built design system from zero, conducted user testing with enterprise compliance managers.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="consult-entry">
        <div class="consult-header">
          <span class="consult-name">Walking the Talk / ZRG Partners &mdash; Product Design Consultant</span>
          <span class="consult-meta">2023 &ndash; 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="consult-desc">Designed UX for the world&rsquo;s largest culture-only consulting firm (40+ countries, 20,000+ survey respondents, acquired by ZRG Partners). Built Taylor Assessment&mdash;the only psychometric tool that measures individual culture contribution across 6 archetypes and 30 behaviors (press-released globally, Jan 2024). Designed Culture Insights Survey (90 behaviors, multi-language, immediate portal results) and Target Culture Mapping tool (80+ executive workshops delivered). Digitalized complex Excel-based workflows into automated software.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="consult-entry">
        <div class="consult-header">
          <span class="consult-name">ADPList &mdash; Product Design Mentor</span>
          <span class="consult-meta">Jan 2024 &ndash; Jan 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="consult-desc">Mentored designers globally on product design, career growth, and portfolio development.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- --- EXPERTISE --- -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Expertise</div>
    <div class="expertise-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="expertise-cat">Design</div>
        <div class="expertise-items">Product Design (Mobile-First) · Design Systems Architecture (Atomic, Token-Based) · Service Design & Blueprinting · User Research (Interviews, Usability, A/B Testing) · Figma · Prototyping</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="expertise-cat">Leadership</div>
        <div class="expertise-items">Design Org Scaling (1&rarr;12) · Hiring Frameworks · Career Progression Design · Design Governance · Workshop Facilitation · C-Suite Stakeholder Management</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="expertise-cat">Domain</div>
        <div class="expertise-items">Payments UX · Digital Wallets · Neobanking · Open Banking · KYC/Onboarding · Compliance &amp; Regulatory (SBP, UAE Open Finance) · Emerging Markets · Crypto/Stablecoins</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="expertise-cat">AI + Design Ops</div>
        <div class="expertise-items">AI-Enabled Design Workflows · Engineer Self-Serve Design · MCP Integrations · Automated Design Operations · Design Knowledge Systems</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- --- EDUCATION --- -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Education</div>
    <div class="edu-row">
      <div>
        <div class="edu-school">University of Engineering &amp; Technology, Taxila</div>
        <div class="edu-degree">B.S. Information Technology &middot; 3.3 CGPA &middot; FYP: Blockchain-based social media application</div>
      </div>
      <span class="edu-year">2014 &ndash; 2018</span>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<script>
  // Mobile top bar visibility
  const mq = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 640px)');
  function handleMobile(e) {
    document.querySelector('.top-bar').style.display = e.matches ? 'flex' : 'none';
  }
  mq.addEventListener('change', handleMobile);
  handleMobile(mq);
</script>

